msgid "We ding this product for no clear retention policy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid "According to the company representative, the data is retained \"until patient requests their data deleted. We often have people who reuse the product after 5+ years.\""
msgstr ""

